sellerCard.oneLiner: Website Designer, Developer :: WordPress, Elementor Ecommerce Expert
sellerCard.description:
My name is ALAMIN.
I am a Web designer and developer, an expert in building custom WordPress websites.
As a Designer and Developer, I have experience working with local clients along with clients from all around the world.
It’s My profession and I do it with a fully professional business point of view to achieve the perfect result.
My works are my identity and I will make sure they will also become the identity of your business.
I design websites after research. All my designs are 100% UNIQUE, EYE CATCHY, and RESPONSIVE.

description.content:
Are you looking for a premium website for your business, corporate agency, or organization?


Then I am the right person to help you to grow more.



Premium Business WordPress Design and Development Services



️ WordPress Installation, Web Customization, and Webpage Creation


️ Custom pages design with Advanced Animations using Elementor Pro


️ Responsive Web Design across all devices (Mobile, Tablet, Desktop)


️ Newsletter or Sign-Up form, Mailchimp, Contact form, Online order form


️ Social links integration, SEO-friendly, Fast and Secure Website Design


️ Bug fixes, Website Backup, Cloning, Migration, Google maps Integration


️ Integration of Payment Gateways in Ecommerce WebSite Development


️ Sliders, Live chat integration, Adobe XD or Figma to WordPress


️ Full Website Redesign, Ecommerce Development using Woocommerce


️ Woocommerce customization, WordPress Development, and much more



Specializations



️ Business, WordPress Blog, Entertainment, Education, Weddings


️ News, Magazine, Landing Pages, Health, Fitness, Woocommerce


️ Ecommerce and Learning Management System using Learndash



Please send me a message for more information

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will You Provide Hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I don't provide domain hosting service with this project but If you need one I can provide hosting services with free SSL certificate integration and 24/7 uptime.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I Able To edit website later?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Even if you don't know any programming language, You can easily edit your website. This is the power of WordPress. I will teach you how to update, edit, and manage your WordPress website by yourself without facing any issues.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What InformationI have to provide to start working?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: (1) Domain & Hosting with Cpanel or wordpress login details (2) Logo (3) Content for Pages (4) List of your services or products

questionsAndAnswers.question: I donot have the contents right now,Can We start?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will add dummy content so that you would be able to replace that with your own content in the future.
